  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919140/extras/c47eaae9543a81bfd88ba246fdf90310.avif?t=1673909990\" width=618 height=320 /></span><br>Play as one of <strong>two detectives working together</strong> to solve an intriguing crime.<br>The adventure will take you to the city of Antioch, a dark metropolis between the mountains and the sea.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919140/extras/6b9be0981b58a9e71f8426aabf4dbb11.avif?t=1673909990\" width=618 height=107 /></span><br>Your partner in the game is a <strong>real person</strong>: a complete stranger or a friend.<br><strong>Both players decide</strong> on the direction of the story - you won't always agree with your partner.<br>How will you <strong>choose</strong> to pursue the case?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919140/extras/1ebe966d2e9dd802d28d7a305807e0a0.avif?t=1673909990\" width=618 height=549 /></span><br>The city is filled with characters with <strong>their own motivations and behaviors</strong>.<br>Discovering their stories (or choosing not to) <strong>will change your experience </strong>of the story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919140/extras/6a5d634137496073c2f1f17a63c32725.avif?t=1673909990\" width=618 height=106 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919140/extras/a639b9fed281af8af4913bbea184b717.avif?t=1673909990\" width=618 height=154 /></span><br>French author <strong>specialized in interactive fiction</strong>, working in different fields such as books where you are the hero, role-playing games, comics and video games. Creator of <strong>Out There</strong> and <strong>Game of Roles</strong>.<br><br>Shape <strong>a unique relationship</strong> between the two protagonists<br>Discover <strong>a dozen different endings</strong> depending on your choices.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919140/extras/e452e663936d8535058ea86553b7f6f0.avif?t=1673909990\" width=618 height=389 /></span><br>The game is fully <strong>multiplatform</strong> <i>(PC / MAC / LINUX - Android / iOS)</i>.<br>Play with your friends or strangers on <strong>all devices</strong>.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919140/extras/88b04dfd590b19000e64b646c06e58de.avif?t=1673909990\" width=618 height=389 /></span><br>",
